*Svestan* je da nema nikakvog povratka, (He is aware that there is no way back.)

On je bio *svestan* njegovih radnji, (He was aware of his actions.)

Ona je bila potpuno *svestna* svojih postupaka, (She was fully aware of her actions.)

On je bio *svesno* odabrao tu stazu, (He consciously chose this path.)

Ona je bila *svesna* da će učiniti nešto nepopularno, (She was aware that she was going to do something unpopular.)